    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CardBurners 是一款快节奏的单人或在线对战卡牌游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须在手牌烧毁之前迅速出牌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手牌会不断堆积，所以你需要快速分析并明智地出牌，否则手牌就会满。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个试玩版允许你进行在线对战，并挑战单人模式中的前几个对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339150/extras/fd6d186bd2e9c03f4eedbf653209d8ff.poster.avif?t=1758703418\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339150/extras/fd6d186bd2e9c03f4eedbf653209d8ff.webm?t=1758703418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339150/extras/fd6d186bd2e9c03f4eedbf653209d8ff.mp4?t=1758703418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >混乱的策略游戏:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人对战 AI 或者和朋友在线对战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由选择节奏，游戏发牌速度最高可达每分钟 100 张。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义规则，混合不同的卡包玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用伤害卡击败对手，让他们抽爆手牌，或者往他们手中埋下炸弹……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样的卡包选择:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个卡包都有截然不同的规则，考验观察力、逻辑或反应力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以单独游玩某个卡包，也能混搭组合创造独特的玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分卡包灵感来自经典纸牌和桌游（花札、疯狂8、抓老 maid）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个卡包都有独特的美术风格，营造出丰富多彩的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团队:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发者: GrosChevaux</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作曲: Billy Palmer - </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音效: Noodle Noise - </p>",
